This repository contains an end-to-end Sales Data Analysis project where I cleaned, transformed, and visualized sales data using AI-powered cleaning, Excel, and Power BI.
The goal of this project is to uncover key business insights such as revenue trends, product performance, regional sales patterns, and customer behavior.

